description: Fallen trees and flooding caused by Storm Francis lead to several road closures on the Isle of Man.
title: Storm Francis: Heavy rain and gales cause Isle of Man travel disruption
title_page: Storm Francis: Heavy rain and gales cause Isle of Man travel disruption - BBC News
maintext: High water levels in the Sulby River led to the closure of Bernaharra Road between its junctions with Lezaye Road and Jurby Road, and Garey Ford remained "impassable", the Department of Infrastructure said.
